ent-graduated students. Perseverance and hard work were the keywords.</p>\"},\"module\":\"paragraph\",\"options\":{},\"styles\":{\"xl\":{\"padding-top\":\"1.1111111111111112rem\"}},\"motions\":{\"active\":[],\"start\":{},\"end\":{}}},\"content_od4iz249m\":{\"content\":{\"xl\":521},\"module\":\"image\",\"options\":{\"align\":\"center\"},\"styles\":{\"xl\":{}},\"motions\":{\"active\":[],\"start\":{},\"end\":{}}},\"column_0xhif30qd\":{\"width\":{\"xl\":\"8\"},\"options\":{},\"layout\":{},\"styles\":{\"xl\":{\"padding-top\":\"2.7777777777777777rem\"},\"xs\":{\"padding-top\":\"1.6666666666666667rem\"}},\"motions\":{\"active\":[],\"start\":{},\"end\":{}}},\"section_78a96357b\":{\"options\":{},\"layout\":{\"data-column-mode-sm\":\"single\",\"data-column-mode-xs\":\"single\",\"data-justify\":\"center\"},\"customHeight\":{\"xl\":{\"height\":\"15rem\"}},\"styles\":{\"xl\":{\"padding-top\":\"4.444444444444445rem\"},\"xs\":{\"padding-top\":\"3.888888888888889rem\"}},\"motions\":{\"active\":{},\"start\":{},\"end\":{}}},\"column_91bdf0ee3\":{\"width\":{\"xl\":\"10\"},\"options\":{},\"layout\":{},\"styles\":{\"xl\":{\"padding-top\":\"0rem\"}},\"motions\":{\"active\":{},\"start\":{},\"end\":{}}},\"content_4ebc36f10\":{\"content\":{\"xl\":\"<p style=\\\"font-size: 1.27778rem; line-height: 1.66667rem;\\\" data-mce-style=\\\"font-size: 1.27778rem; line-height: 1.66667rem;\\\"><span style=\\\"color: rgb(246, 60, 59);\\\" data-mce-style=\\\"color: #f63c3b;\\\">In&nbsp;October</span> we conquered the fashion world…</p>\",\"xs\":\"<p style=\\\"font-size: 1.44444rem; line-height: 1.72222rem;\\\" data-mce-style=\\\"font-size: 1.44444rem; line-height: 1.72222rem;\\\"><span class=\\\"font_pv7ryu5ou\\\"><span style=\\\"color: rgb(246, 60, 59);\\\" data-mce-style=\\\"color: #f63c3b;\\\">In&nbsp;October</span> <span style=\\\"color: rgb(86, 86, 86);\\\" data-mce-style=\\\"color: #565656;\\\">we conquered the</span> fashion world…</span></p>\"},\"module\":\"paragraph\",\"options\":{},\"styles\":{\"xl\":{}},\"motions\":{\"active\":{},\"start\":{},\"end\":{}}},\"content_1839ded40\":{\"content\":{\"xl\":\"<p style=\\\"line-height: 1.27778rem;\\\" data-mce-style=\\\"line-height: 1.27778rem;\\\">From internet to television, we placed <span class=\\\"font_rke3axlo6\\\"><a data-mce-href=\\\"https://mintysquare.com/\\\" href=\\\"https://mintysquare.com/\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener\\\">Minty Square</a></span>, a Portuguese emergent designers platform, on everyone’s lips… and since then its founders Ana Cravo and João Figueiredo are overwhelmed with the requests to share their testimony about how they’re changing Portuguese designers market.</p><p style=\\\"line-height: 0.555556rem;\\\" data-mce-style=\\\"line-height: 0.555556rem;\\\"><a data-mce-href=\\\"http://sicnoticias.sapo.pt/pais/2017-12-19-Uma-plataforma-online-para-divulgar-designers-portugueses\\\" href=\\\"http://sicnoticias.sapo.pt/pais/2017-12-19-Uma-plataforma-online-para-divulgar-designers-portugueses\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener\\\">Sic Notícias</a></p><p style=\\\"line-height: 0.555556rem;\\\" data-mce-style=\\\"line-height: 0.555556rem;\\\"><a data-mce-href=\\\"https://www.publico.pt/2017/12/29/culto/noticia/minty-square-1796723\\\" href=\\\"https://www.publico.pt/2017/12/29/culto/noticia/minty-square-1796723\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener\\\" data-mce-selected=\\\"1\\\">Público</a></p>\"},\"module\":\"paragraph\",\"options\":{},\"styles\":{\"xl\":{\"padding-top\":\"1.1111111111111112rem\"}},\"motions\":{\"active\":{},\"start\":{},\"end\":{}}},\"content_4375de2f1\":{\"content\":{\"xl\":520},\"module\":\"image\",\"options\":{\"align\":\"center\"},\"styles\":{\"xl\":{\"padding-top\":\"0rem\"}},\"motions\":{\"active\":{},\"start\":{},\"end\":{}}},\"section_b49f5635c\":{\"options\":{},\"layout\":{\"data-column-mode-sm\":\"single\",\"data-column-mode-xs\":\"single\",\"data-justify\":\"center\"},\"customHeight\":{\"xl\":{\"height\":\"15rem\"}},\"styles\":{\"xl\":{\"padding-top\":\"4.444444444444445rem\"},\"xs\":{\"padding-top\":\"3.888888888888889rem\"}},\"motions\":{\"active\":{},\"start\":{},\"end\":{}}},\"column_9f2ff001d\":{\"width\":{\"xl\":\"10\"},\"options\":{},\"layout\":{},\"styles\":{\"xl\":{\"padding-top\":\"0rem\"}},\"motions\":{\"active\":{},\"start\":{},\"end\":{}}},\"content_08655511a\":{\"content\":{\"xl\":\"<p style=\\\"font-size: 1.27778rem; line-height: 1.66667rem;\\\" data-mce-style=\\\"font-size: 1.27778rem; line-height: 1.66667rem;\\\"><span style=\\\"color: rgb(246, 60, 59);\\\" data-mce-style=\\\"color: #f63c3b;\\\">In&nbsp;November</span>, we got out of The Square to visit the Web Summit… &nbsp;</p>\",\"xs\":\"<p style=\\\"font-size: 1.44444rem; line-height: 1.72222rem;\\\" data-mce-style=\\\"font-size: 1.44444rem; line-height: 1.72222rem;\\\"><span class=\\\"font_pv7ryu5ou\\\"><span style=\\\"color: rgb(246, 60, 59);\\\" data-mce-style=\\\"color: #f63c3b;\\\">In&nbsp;November,</span> we got out of The Square<span style=\\\"color: rgb(86, 86, 86);\\\" data-mce-style=\\\"color: #565656;\\\"> to visit the Web Summit… &nbsp;</span></span></p>\"},\"module\":\"paragraph\",\"options\":{},\"styles\":{\"xl\":{}},\"motions\":{\"active\":{},\"start\":{},\"end\":{}}},\"content_6bcb693e4\":{\"content\":{\"xl\":\"<p style=\\\"line-height: 1.27778rem;\\\" data-mce-style=\\\"line-height: 1.27778rem;\\\">Entrepreneurial spirit and resilience to walk the path of stones are part of our DNA. So, we couldn’t miss the biggest conference on technology and entrepreneurship in the world.</p><p style=\\\"line-height: 1.27778rem;\\\" data-mce-style=\\\"line-height: 1.27778rem;\\\">As we didn’t have the chance to take part in the meetings, we decided to stand out in a more creative way: we took The Square to the Web Summit. We took advantage of our PR capacities and showed to global startups and big companies what we do best: placing great companies and ideas on the most relevant media outlets.</p><p style=\\\"line-height: 1.27