) news to share!</p><p style=\\\"line-height: 1.27778rem;\\\" data-mce-style=\\\"line-height: 1.27778rem;\\\">See you soon,</p><p style=\\\"line-height: 1.27778rem;\\\" data-mce-style=\\\"line-height: 1.27778rem;\\\">The Square Team</p>\",\"xs\":\"<p style=\\\"line-height: 1.27778rem;\\\" data-mce-style=\\\"line-height: 1.27778rem;\\\">Everything started last Summer. The “bug” for entrepreneurship was asleep, but it finally woke up. Since the very beginning, we wanted a simple office where we could do things well and with a lot of passion.</p><p style=\\\"line-height: 1.27778rem;\\\" data-mce-style=\\\"line-height: 1.27778rem;\\\">Becoming one of the most respectful communication offices in Portugal is our medium-term goal and we know that only with a strong team of fighters this can be possible. We love what we do, and we want to add real and measurable value to our clients.</p>\"},\"module\":\"paragraph\",\"options\":{},\"styles\":{\"xl\":{\"padding-top\":\"1.1111111111111112rem\"},\"xs\":{\"padding-top\":\"1.1111111111111112rem\"}},\"motions\":{\"active\":[],\"start\":{},\"end\":{}}},\"section_fca3d4560\":{\"options\":{},\"layout\":{\"data-column-mode-sm\":\"single\",\"data-column-mode-xs\":\"single\",\"data-justify\":\"center\"},\"customHeight\":{\"xl\":{\"height\":\"15rem\"}},\"styles\":{\"xl\":{\"padding-top\":\"0rem\",\"padding-bottom\":\"4.444444444444445rem\"}},\"motions\":{\"active\":{},\"start\":{},\"end\":{}}},\"column_c1ea9b154\":{\"width\":{\"xl\":\"10\"},\"options\":{},\"layout\":{},\"styles\":{\"xl\":{\"padding-top\":\"0rem\"}},\"motions\":{\"active\":{},\"start\":{},\"end\":{}}},\"content_ef97a8fdd\":{\"content\":{\"xl\":\"<p style=\\\"font-size: 1.27778rem; line-height: 1.72222rem;\\\" data-mce-style=\\\"font-size: 1.27778rem; line-height: 1.72222rem;\\\"><span style=\\\"color: rgb(246, 60, 59);\\\" data-mce-style=\\\"color: #f63c3b;\\\">Beatriz</span> came to revolutionize The Square</p>\"},\"module\":\"paragraph\",\"options\":{},\"styles\":{\"xl\