	(2910,828,'descricao','From\r\n<h3>Azores</h3>\r\nto The Square….\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.66667rem;\"><strong>Graduated in Business Administration from the University of Coimbra</strong> with a postgraduate degree in Marketing Management from Instituto Universitário de Lisboa. While studying, Sara spent 6 years in student associativism and started her career in PR with scientific communication. She has also worked at a sports federation and at a multinational video game company.</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.66667rem;\">At The Square she focuses in tech and entrepreneurship. She is constantly surprised by the innovators that she meets. Sara quickly learned how to achieve great results: great discipline, humility, talent, persistence, passion and teamwork.</p>'),
