	(2923,830,'descricao','From\r\n<h3>Madeira</h3>\r\n(&amp; Lisbon) to The Square….\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.66667rem;\"><strong>Her artistic side took her to Representation, at ACT, Escola de Atores</strong>, but quickly Communication gained her attention: Ângela is graduated in Communication and Culture from the Faculty of Humanities of Lisbon and holds a post-graduation in Communication and Content Marketing from Catholic University. She has worked for some of the most relevant Portuguese media groups as a journalist. She has also led the communication of a real estate agency, with focus on digital.</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.66667rem;\">Methodical and dedicated, Ângela ventured into the Public Relations world with The Square, but she says she could be a carpenter too.</p>'),
