	(2936,832,'descricao','From\r\n<h3>São Paulo</h3>\r\n(&amp; Lisbon) to The Square….\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.66667rem;\"><strong>Graduated in Strategic Communication, Advertising and Public Relations from the Universidade da Beira Interior</strong>. Ana took part in a communication project created with some classmates whilst in college and her first professional steps started at a Public Relations agency. Ana is also experienced in working in trade marketing, mostly with brands from the fashion industry.</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.66667rem;\">Ana can be described as a perfectionist, hardworking and a lover of pop culture.</p>'),
