	(2958,835,'descricao','From\r\n<h3>Figueira da Foz</h3>\r\n(&amp; Lisbon) to The Square….\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.66667rem;\"><strong>Cristiana is graduated in Social Communication from School of Education of Coimbra and post graduated in Public Relations Strategic Management from School of Communication and Media Studies</strong>. She started her career in journalism. She was also an audio producer, mostly in publicity.</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.66667rem;\">Cristiana is a naturally communicative person, adventurous and focused on concrete results. For her, surfing is the best therapy to leave the stress behind and reload.</p>'),
