	(3019,843,'about_text','<h2 class=\"tax-ttile tax-title\">It’s a square… an (almost)</h2>\r\n<h2 class=\"tax-ttile tax-title\"><span class=\"red\">regular square…</span></h2>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>It’s a Square, but not a simple Square.\r\n</strong><strong>It’s a Square where almost everything is possible. </strong>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nUnicorns in magazine covers, Walking Libraries on cars, Witch\'s Drool and Bone Cream on national tv, Solidarity Lockers around the city… costumer experience is a must…\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nThis is a Square full of work, dedication and commitment.\r\n\r\nAnd also a Square full of creativity, proximity and joy.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nIt’s a Square, but not a simple Square. For us, the sky is the limit, almost like an open square.\r\n\r\nIt’s a Square because it was born in a square.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nIt’s a Square because we want to prove that PR can be done with “(almost) regular ideas”, where the execution and storyteling make the difference, and with measurable impact.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nIt’s a Square where PR, influence, digital and content marketing reign.\r\n\r\nWe love content and storytelling.'),
