 Our DNA is all about fighting to make dreams come true and to celebrate and value each achievement. And it was with this spirit, a smile on the face and willing to win, that…</p>\"},\"module\":\"paragraph\",\"options\":{},\"styles\":{\"xl\":{}},\"motions\":{\"active\":[],\"start\":{},\"end\":{}}},\"section_toz597351\":{\"options\":{},\"layout\":{\"data-column-mode-sm\":\"single\",\"data-column-mode-xs\":\"single\",\"data-justify\":\"center\"},\"customHeight\":{\"xl\":{\"height\":\"15rem\"}},\"styles\":{\"xl\":{\"padding-top\":\"5.555555555555555rem\",\"padding-bottom\":\"4.444444444444445rem\"},\"xs\":{\"padding-bottom\":\"2.7777777777777777rem\",\"padding-top\":\"2.7777777777777777rem\"}},\"motions\":{\"active\":[],\"start\":{},\"end\":{}}},\"column_vlq9g44bq\":{\"width\":{\"xl\":\"10\"},\"options\":{},\"layout\":{},\"styles\":{\"xl\":{\"padding-top\":\"0rem\",\"padding-bottom\":\"0rem\"}},\"motions\":{\"active\":[],\"start\":{},\"end\":{}}},\"content_6c8c007d9\":{\"content\":{\"xl\":\"<p>Soon we will have more (good) news to share!</p><p>See you soon,</p><p>The Square Team</p>\",\"xs\":\"<p style=\\\"line-height: 1.27778rem;\\\" data-mce-style=\\\"line-height: 1.27778rem;\\\">Everything started last Summer. The “bug” for entrepreneurship was asleep, but it finally woke up. Since the very beginning, we wanted a simple office where we could do things well and with a lot of passion.</p><p style=\\\"line-height: 1.27778rem;\\\" data-mce-style=\\\"line-height: 1.27778rem;\\\">Becoming one of the most respectful communication offices in Portugal is our medium-term goal and we know that only with a strong team of fighters this can be possible. We love what we do, and we want to add real and measurable value to our clients.</p>\"},\"module\":\"paragraph\",\"options\":{},\"styles\":{\"xl\":{\"padding-top\":\"0rem\",\"padding-bottom\":\"0rem\"},\"xs\":{\"padding-top\":\"1.1111111111111112rem\"}},\"motions\":{\"active\":[],\"start\":{},\"end\":{}}},\"content_5mei5sbci\":{\"