g for in recent-graduated students. Perseverance and hard work were the keywords.</p>\"},\"module\":\"paragraph\",\"options\":{},\"styles\":{\"xl\":{\"padding-top\":\"1.1111111111111112rem\"}},\"motions\":{\"active\":[],\"start\":{},\"end\":{}}},\"content_od4iz249m\":{\"content\":{\"xl\":521},\"module\":\"image\",\"options\":{\"align\":\"center\"},\"styles\":{\"xl\":{}},\"motions\":{\"active\":[],\"start\":{},\"end\":{}}},\"column_0xhif30qd\":{\"width\":{\"xl\":\"8\"},\"options\":{},\"layout\":{},\"styles\":{\"xl\":{\"padding-top\":\"2.7777777777777777rem\"},\"xs\":{\"padding-top\":\"1.6666666666666667rem\"}},\"motions\":{\"active\":[],\"start\":{},\"end\":{}}},\"section_78a96357b\":{\"options\":{},\"layout\":{\"data-column-mode-sm\":\"single\",\"data-column-mode-xs\":\"single\",\"data-justify\":\"center\"},\"customHeight\":{\"xl\":{\"height\":\"15rem\"}},\"styles\":{\"xl\":{\"padding-top\":\"4.444444444444445rem\"},\"xs\":{\"padding-top\":\"3.888888888888889rem\"}},\"motions\":{\"active\":{},\"start\":{},\"end\":{}}},\"column_91bdf0ee3\":{\"width\":{\"xl\":\"10\"},\"options\":{},\"layout\":{},\"styles\":{\"xl\":{\"padding-top\":\"0rem\"}},\"motions\":{\"active\":{},\"start\":{},\"end\":{}}},\"content_4ebc36f10\":{\"content\":{\"xl\":\"<p style=\\\"font-size: 1.27778rem; line-height: 1.66667rem;\\\" data-mce-style=\\\"font-size: 1.27778rem; line-height: 1.66667rem;\\\"><span style=\\\"color: rgb(246, 60, 59);\\\" data-mce-style=\\\"color: #f63c3b;\\\">In&nbsp;October</span> we conquered the fashion world…</p>\",\"xs\":\"<p style=\\\"font-size: 1.44444rem; line-height: 1.72222rem;\\\" data-mce-style=\\\"font-size: 1.44444rem; line-height: 1.72222rem;\\\"><span class=\\\"font_pv7ryu5ou\\\"><span style=\\\"color: rgb(246, 60, 59);\\\" data-mce-style=\\\"color: #f63c3b;\\\">In&nbsp;October</span> <span style=\\\"color: rgb(86, 86, 86);\\\" data-mce-style=\\\"color: #565656;\\\">we conquered the</span> fashion world…</span></p>\"},\"module\":\"paragraph\",\"options\":{},